  "texts": [
    "The proliferation of data on the Internet combined with the exponential growth in computing capacity and the discovery of a more capable language model architecture led to a tipping point in the performance of AI chatbots.",
    "This primer provided a comprehensive and accessible tutorial on large language models (LLMs) such as ChatGPT and Google's Bard.",
    "The goal was to demystify their underlying theory, architecture, and methods for a broad audience.",
    "The primer provided insights into key computing elements, architectural choices, and state-of-the-art training methods that have enabled these models to achieve groundbreaking performance.",
    "The new ability to use only natural language for interaction has significantly increased the accessibility of computers, which will pave the way for an explosion of novel applications across various domains."
